    "question_id" : 5993779,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Using <a href=\"http://guava-libraries.googlecode.com\">Guava</a> you could do this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Iterable&lt;String&gt; tokens = Splitter.on(CharMatcher.anyOf(\"-.\")).split(pdfName);\n</code></pre>\n"
